      "subject": "Application: Senior AI Engineer - Sarah Jenkins",
      "body": {
        "contentType": "html",
        "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Hello Recruiting Team,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">I&nbsp;am writing to express my strong interest in the Senior AI Engineer position at Hermes AI, as advertised on LinkedIn.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">With over 6 years of experience building and deploying scalable Large Language Model (LLM) agents, orchestration systems, and custom RAG pipelines, I am confident in my ability to contribute to your advanced intelligence pipeline products.</span><span style=\"color:rgb(215,186,125)\">\\n\\n</span><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">I have attached my resume detailing my accomplishments at TechCorp, where I led the developer platform team and optimized agent token latency by 45%.</span><span style=\"color:rgb(215,186,125)\">\\n\\n</span><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing from you regarding potential next steps.</span><span style=\"color:rgb(215,186,125)\">\\n\\n</span><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Sincerely,</span><span style=\"color:rgb(215,186,125)\">\\n</span><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Sarah Jenkins</span><span style=\"color:rgb(215,186,125)\">\\n</span><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Phone: (555) 019-2834</span><span style=\"color:rgb(215,186,125)\">\\n</span><span style=\"color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Website: sarahcodes.dev&quot;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(204,204,204)\">,</span></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><br></div>Disclaimer: This message contains information which is confidential and protected by copyright and is governed by intellectual property rights of Crisp Analytics Pvt Ltd (Lumiq). The use of the \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d trademarks without the prior written consent of \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d is forbidden. If you are not the intended recipient of this message, please delete it and destroy all copies. If you are the intended recipient of this message, you should not disclose or distribute or forward it to third parties without the consent of our company. </body></html>"
      }
