    "full_msg": {
      "@odata.context": "https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/$metadata#users('e9b935fa-f52f-448f-acb3-ee7e18a0147b')/messages(body,subject)/$entity",
      "@odata.etag": "W/\"CQAAABYAAADWbvNAZXc9SoXua9mRWwANAAACd5ik\"",
      "id": "AAMkADJlNTFlMmYyLTI2YWQtNGI2Zi05OWRhLTg0OGUwYzEyNDYwZQBGAAAAAACEFbGlA20DRrZnMCfJtQMWBwDWbvNAZXc9SoXua9mRWwANAAAAAAEMAADWbvNAZXc9SoXua9mRWwANAAACenByAAA=",
      "subject": "CRITICAL: Major Production Downtime due to API Interruption",
      "body": {
        "contentType": "html",
        "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div style=\"background-color:rgb(31,31,31)\"><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Hi Hermes Team,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">I am writing to express my severe disappointment with the service reliability today. We experienced a complete interruption of the Hermes Classification API between 2:00 PM and 3:30 PM EST.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">This API is integrated directly into our real-time manufacturing dispatch line. Because of the outage, our sorting systems ground to a halt, resulting in 90 minutes of idling labor and a backlog of over 4,000 unclassified shipments. This downtime has cost us roughly $25,000 in immediate logistical delays.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">We require an immediate root-cause analysis (RCA) and want to know how you plan to compensate us under our Enterprise SLA guidelines.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Regards,</div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Derek Vaughn</div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">VP of Global Operations, GlobalFab Logistics</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><br></div>Disclaimer: This message contains information which is confidential and protected by copyright and is governed by intellectual property rights of Crisp Analytics Pvt Ltd (Lumiq). The use of the \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d trademarks without the prior written consent of \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d is forbidden. If you are not the intended recipient of this message, please delete it and destroy all copies. If you are the intended recipient of this message, you should not disclose or distribute or forward it to third parties without the consent of our company. </body></html>"
      }
    }
