    "full_msg": {
      "@odata.context": "https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/$metadata#users('e9b935fa-f52f-448f-acb3-ee7e18a0147b')/messages(body,subject)/$entity",
      "@odata.etag": "W/\"CQAAABYAAADWbvNAZXc9SoXua9mRWwANAAACd5gj\"",
      "id": "AAMkADJlNTFlMmYyLTI2YWQtNGI2Zi05OWRhLTg0OGUwYzEyNDYwZQBGAAAAAACEFbGlA20DRrZnMCfJtQMWBwDWbvNAZXc9SoXua9mRWwANAAAAAAEMAADWbvNAZXc9SoXua9mRWwANAAACenBxAAA=",
      "subject": "Enterprise Partnership Proposal - InnovateTech & Hermes AI",
      "body": {
        "contentType": "html",
        "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div style=\"background-color:rgb(31,31,31)\"><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Dear Executive Team,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">I&nbsp;hope this email finds you well.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">I am Marcus Vance, VP of Business Development at InnovateTech. We specialize in deploying enterprise AI frameworks for Fortune 500 financial institutions.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">We have been following Hermes AI's breakthroughs in autonomous email decision pipelines. We see a significant synergy in integrating the Hermes Agentic Engine into our core banking compliance dashboards to automate audit classifications.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">We would like to explore an enterprise strategic partnership. Are you available for a 15-minute briefing session this Thursday at 2:00 PM EST to discuss potential technical integration pathways?</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Sincerely,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Marcus Vance</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">BP, Business Development</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">InnovateTech Corporation</div></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><br></div>Disclaimer: This message contains information which is confidential and protected by copyright and is governed by intellectual property rights of Crisp Analytics Pvt Ltd (Lumiq). The use of the \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d trademarks without the prior written consent of \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d is forbidden. If you are not the intended recipient of this message, please delete it and destroy all copies. If you are the intended recipient of this message, you should not disclose or distribute or forward it to third parties without the consent of our company. </body></html>"
