      "subject": "Next Steps: Kickoff meeting setup for CareHealth Onboarding",
      "body": {
        "contentType": "html",
        "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div style=\"background-color:rgb(31,31,31)\"><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Hello Hermes Success Team,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">I&nbsp;am thrilled to report that our board has fully executed the Master Services Agreement this morning! CareHealth is officially a Hermes AI enterprise partner.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">We want to hit the ground running. What are our immediate next steps to coordinate the technical integration kickoff?</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Specifically, could you share the developer onboarding documentation and let us know what technical resources (e.g. system access, cloud permissions) our infrastructure team needs to provision prior to our kickoff call?</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Looking forward to a great collaboration!</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Best,</div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Nathan Ross</div><div style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">VP of Engineering, CareHealth</div></div>Disclaimer: This message contains information which is confidential and protected by copyright and is governed by intellectual property rights of Crisp Analytics Pvt Ltd (Lumiq). The use of the \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d trademarks without the prior written consent of \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d is forbidden. If you are not the intended recipient of this message, please delete it and destroy all copies. If you are the intended recipient of this message, you should not disclose or distribute or forward it to third parties without the consent of our company. </body></html>"
      }
    }
