      "subject": "Contract Feedback: Enterprise Licensing Tiers and Pricing Inquiry",
      "body": {
        "contentType": "html",
        "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div style=\"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Hello Hermes Sales Team,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">We have completed our evaluation of the Hermes Email Intelligence platform and are highly satisfied with the pipeline capabilities. Our legal and operations teams are ready to move forward.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">However, the custom pricing schedule sent over by your account executive ($45,000 annually for 20 seats) exceeds our budget cap for operational tools this quarter by roughly 20%.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">We are looking to secure licensing for 15 seats instead, or want to know if you can offer a 15% discount on the 20-seat package if we sign a multi-year (3-year) contract commit.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\"><br></div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Please let us know if we can adjust these licensing parameters so we can proceed with execution this week.</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">est,</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Clara Peters</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; text-align:left; text-indent:0px; line-height:18px; text-transform:none; background-color:rgb(31,31,31); font-family:Menlo,Monaco,&quot;Courier New&quot;,monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgb(206,145,120)\">Head of Procurement, RetailGiant</div><div style=\"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><br></div><div id=\"ms-outlook-mobile-signature\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color:inherit; background-color:inherit\"><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"direction:ltr\"><br></div></div>Disclaimer: This message contains information which is confidential and protected by copyright and is governed by intellectual property rights of Crisp Analytics Pvt Ltd (Lumiq). The use of the \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d trademarks without the prior written consent of \u201cLumiq.ai\u201d is forbidden. If you are not the intended recipient of this message, please delete it and destroy all copies. If you are the intended recipient of this message, you should not disclose or distribute or forward it to third parties without the consent of our company. </body></html>"
